{{Orphan|date=July 2014}}


'''Nyakélé''' is a very small town in the [[Littoral Region (Cameroon)|Littoral Region]] of [[Cameroon]], on the content of [[Africa]]. It belongs to the [[Sanaga-Maritime]] [[Departments of Cameroon|department]] whose capital is [[Edéa|Édéa]].

Small neighboring towns include; Ngakélé, [[Nyanon]], Nyoudem and Pendiki, while the major neighboring cities include; [[Yaoundé]], [[Edéa|Édéa]], [[Douala]] and [[Bafoussam]].<ref>{{Cite web|title = Where is Nyakele in Littoral, Cameroon located?|url = http://www.gomapper.com/travel/where-is/nyakele-located.html|website = www.gomapper.com|accessdate = 2015-07-13}}</ref>

